snippet.title: BIWAR LEGEND OF DRAGON SLAYER Reveal Trailer (2023) 4K
snippet.description:
Biwar Legend of Dragon Slayer Official Reveal Trailer New in remastered/upscaled 4K ULTRA HD for PC, PS4, XBOX ONE and in smooth 60 FPS.

Release Date: 2023

Biwar Legend Of Dragon Slayer is an upcoming action adventure puzzle use the Magic Mechanic such a : Telekinesis Power, Agni and Toya Elements, and Non Euclidean puzzles. The game is being developed by Devata Game Production.

Wishlist on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1680800/Biwar_Legend_of_Dragon_Slayer/
